1. k version => to get cluster verison 
2. k get node => to get info about the cluster nodes
3. k get node -o wide => to get more info about the cluster nodes
4. k get pod => to get info about cluster pods
5. k get pod -o wide => to get more info about cluster pods
6. k run <podname> --image <imagename> => to run a pod
7. k describe pod <podname> => to get all info about a specific pod
8. k delete pod <podname> => to delete a pod
